profile_summary: I'm Afsheen Aziz, a skilled software developer with expertise in back-end development using Python, with a strong foundation in C++ and versatile front-end skills in CSS. I've developed and contributed to a wide range of projects across various domains, leveraging my problem-solving abilities and software craftsmanship. With over a decade of experience in delivering high-quality solutions and collaborating with peers to achieve shared goals, I continue to grow and improve as a developer.
